{"tid":187488,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[on9仔 369]售兩支雙飛人藥水收5萬元 藥房店員待索智力評估報告","createTime":"2017-04-05T04:15:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-05T07:35:04.000Z","uid":987,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b154abc3b352c7fd7cf8fb575fa869bf064f3be","tid":187488,"uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T04:15:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170405/large/1491359991_62ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170405%2Flarge%2F1491359991_62ba.jpg&h=b7c9cfe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n六旬內地婦前年到旺角一藥坊購買兩支共值60元的法國雙飛人藥水，卻遭店員用信用卡過數5萬元。兩名年輕男店員早前經審訊後，被裁定欺詐罪成，裁判官原定今判刑，惟報告建議替其中一人索取智力評估報告，裁判官擔心或影響其求情，決定跟隨建議另索閱報告，押後判刑。<br />\n<br />\n九龍城法院暫委裁判官梁禮賢閱讀兩名被告梁家葆（20歲）及鄧子豪（23歲）的青少年罪犯評估委員會報告後，指報告建議再索取感化報告，但梁官指不會考慮，惟最終按報告建議，為梁索取教導所、為鄧索取勞教、心理及智力評估報告，兩人續還柙至本月26日判刑。<br />\n<br />\n鄧的大律師求情指他案發後沒再工作，靠母親供養，案件亦被傳媒廣泛報道，令他對母親的歉疚更大。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指兩名被告前年11月29日在旺角西洋菜南街「龍興中西藥坊」犯案。<img src=\"http://staticlayout.apple.nextmedia.com/web_images/layout/art_end.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstaticlayout.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fweb_images%2Flayout%2Fart_end.gif&h=10b8c7d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170405/56523485\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170405%2F56523485&d=e9hI6ag5UTzhCSVhase9yGMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=54bf2ce8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170405%2F56523485&h=b83f1c92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170405/56523485</a><br />\n<br />\n人地叫你做就做呀，收人咁撚貴，抵撚死，on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"456fa41f4a399e2854a42e44bc335a8adcfc4701","tid":187488,"uid":3682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T04:29:51.000Z","msg":"弱智仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a1d3ea3ab86e0b8b41399f9211368a433344d32","tid":187488,"uid":32676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T04:45:20.000Z","msg":"on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd3d32daa77ee30756f6f44bfc6ea6a7f8d946a0","tid":187488,"uid":35919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T04:52:04.000Z","msg":"on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a4ebaec592d52628d1067e39310ab2a79cb692","tid":187488,"uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T05:04:15.000Z","msg":"咁撚弱智，唔洗拎智力評估都知係低能嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf95a7c55aa4ffa1e94a08351ee387d5275ae9b","tid":187488,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T05:05:21.000Z","msg":"20 23歲仲都叫青年"},{"pid":"c521a5edd04f0b523784e655b04fc6e0568281eb","tid":187488,"uid":29273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T05:07:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>20 23歲仲都叫青年</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n40歲可以拎傑出青年"},{"pid":"42e05b32a11280847c01ed6fecb51691a460bed1","tid":187488,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T05:23:24.000Z","msg":"60蚊都碌卡，抵撚死！"},{"pid":"8f73395fd4ade70ab7f554ba